					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">tepples wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">But the nonlinear response and phosphor colors of a TV tube are similar to the nonlinear response and phosphor colors of a PC CRT monitor, right?</div>Yes. Don't let anyone tell you something about "NTSC primaries"; they're not used by any TV made after 1960 or so.</div>

